    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a weekend getaway! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s clean, comfortable, and totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
